analysis_general: "easy going" can be subjective and may implicitly favor certain cultural behaviors or personality types. "MUST HAVE COMMON SENSE!" and noting that "this isn't something we can teach, you either have it or you don't" introduces a highly subjective criterion. What is considered common sense can vary widely between different cultures, backgrounds, and personal experiences.
